{"id": "1204833311952871434", "channel_id": "1204833311952871434", "type": 0, "author_id": "790789436664578138", "author_name": "like72127", "author_bot": false, "content": "症状:呓语+症状:癔想+融灾5时灵摆+蝴蝶标本≈≈对凯科斯无敌。\n融灾5时灵摆出牌就能触发回血效果，回血效果在触发蝴蝶标本给盾，基本上能做到血量盾量很安全。\n配置(附图)\n叠到1000力量(附图3)\n80回合截图(附图4)\nboss战中间部分过程(就一个6秒视频)。\n只是想分享一下快乐，不是很实用，快乐就完了！", "timestamp": "2024-02-07T16:57:26.290000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-07T16:57:52.280000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1204833312234020946", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-16-28-794_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 90259, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204833311952871434/1204833312234020946/Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-16-28-794_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfcf6&is=69caab76&hm=af055a3f641d74fe5877056afb3980192f47ef1a7f55da514d442783233234ee&"}, {"id": "1204833312523157595", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-07-20-16-29-161_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 120436, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204833311952871434/1204833312523157595/Screenshot_2024-02-07-20-16-29-161_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfcf6&is=69caab76&hm=64fd4b742e0611d6787223eac4207ecaead480a21419db6538784de0222023c7&"}, {"id": "1204833312783466566", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-42-42-889_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 205007, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204833311952871434/1204833312783466566/Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-42-42-889_com.miui.video.jpg?ex=69cbfcf6&is=69caab76&hm=062cf0e26c4982a2d28e58df8c1f5cd0de2ce1abc69e53560f164e5a9c611e13&"}, {"id": "1204833313034870804", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-20-42-858_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 207673, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204833311952871434/1204833313034870804/Screenshot_2024-02-08-00-20-4