{"id": "1204879363393454161", "channel_id": "1204879363393454161", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "老規矩，活動地圖依舊加入踩一次掉血量上限5%的紫色毒地板，而且部分地圖是必經之路必須踩。這次更多的需要走回頭路，當然不回頭直接打最終戰也可以。雖然這次劇情很碎，但是非必經之路上沒有劇情。\n這次的地圖形狀變得具象了起來，除了第二張地圖比較像鑰匙，其他就比較抽象但是總感覺是什麼東西。uid100001547\n#彌薩格大學攻略募集三期\n說到劇情這邊也放一個活動純劇情剪輯的視頻地址，方便大家觀看【【忘却前夜Morimens】特遣记录合集 | 纯剧情向-哔哩哔哩】 https://b23.tv/F4RtXVB", "timestamp": "2024-02-07T20:00:25.809000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-27T09:52:39.737000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1204879364890562641", "filename": "Image_1707335105205.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3071705, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204879363393454161/1204879364890562641/Image_1707335105205.jpg?ex=69cc27da&is=69cad65a&hm=1d54110645c517a4b9206a8f0b9d14a79407b3a215c66adf523ac739d4a0f2fc&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "link", "title": "最圆满的结局_哔哩哔哩_bilibili", "url": "https://b23.tv/F4RtXVB", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204879363393454161", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "故事的魔法 地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1204779995587682354", "channel_id": "1204779995587682354", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "劇本迷思限時活動開啟，該活動沒有和其他遊戲一樣特別在主界面開闢一個明顯的區塊，具體入口在主界面左下角 福利-故事的魔法 進入（此界面右下角）。\n活動的地圖、事件、敵人等是隨機的，然後地圖應該是3張，如圖。\n體力藥不急著磕，完全來得及，70級害怕也就攢幾瓶復活藥就行。uid100001547\n#彌薩格大學攻略募集三期", "timestamp": "2024-02-07T13:25:34.678000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-27T09:53:47.441000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1204779996477132830", "filename": "Image_1707311408898.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1514173, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204779995587682354/1204779996477132830/Image_1707311408898.jpg?ex=69cbcb4e&is=69ca79ce&hm=7ed94c12174b08706354b13d95e94fc8c3fa943bb2581b7242d6c439df1c978d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204779995587682354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "劇本迷思地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
